      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesnt feel like a coincidence though. i mean, the timing was too perfect and the details were identical. like, the same scratch on the cup? i've been reading about how simulations have to reuse assets to save on processing power when the environment gets too complex. if i keep seeing these 'repeats', doesnt that imply the simulation is hitting a limit?",
